Package chessapi4j

Enum Square

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Square>
      • chessapi4j.Square
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Square>
    public enum Square
extends Enum<Square>
    Basis enum for squares. Ordinal order follows regular convention where A1 is 0, B1 is 1 and so on.
    Since:
    1.2.3
    Author:
    Migue
